OL,3,CHospital without drinking water for
OL,4,Csixth day in a row
OL,6,FA hospital in Kent is without drinking
OL,7,Fwater for the sixth day in a row.
OL,9,FDarent Valley Hospital in Dartford
OL,10,Ffirst experienced issues on 29 April.
OL,12,FThe NHS Trust has posted on its
OL,13,Fwebsite that it is "currently managing
OL,14,Fa water supply issue affecting parts
OL,15,Fof the hospital."
OL,17,FAs a precaution it is asking patient,
OL,18,Fstaff and visitors to not drink water
OL,19,Ffrom taps or use it for washing in the
OL,20,Faffected areas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
