OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1777978995
OL,3,CHospital without drinking water for
OL,4,Csixth day in a row
OL,6,FThe hospital says affected areas will
OL,7,Fhave clear labels on taps to remind
OL,8,Fpeople not to use them and that
OL,9,Falternative arrangements have been put
OL,10,Fin place.
OL,12,FThe Trust says it hopes to resolve the
OL,13,Fsituation as quickly as possible and
OL,14,Fhas thanked people for their
OL,15,Funderstanding and cooperation.
OL,17,FIt's believed an internal fault is to
OL,18,Fblame for the problem which is
OL,19,Faffecting the west block of the
OL,20,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
